          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            BreederHQ does not verify, vet, or vouch for breeders or providers. What appears on a profile comes from three layers buyers can see and weigh for themselves.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-10">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-stone-200">
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 font-semibold mb-2">Layer 1</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Identity confirmation (Stripe Identity)</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Stripe Identity, a service operated by Stripe, Inc., checks a government-issued photo ID. The profile shows <em>&ldquo;Identity confirmed via Stripe Identity&rdquo;</em> with the date.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-stone-200">
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 font-semibold mb-2">Layer 2</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Public-registry passthrough</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              For credentials issued by organizations with a public registry (OFA, AKC, AFA, state licensing boards), the profile may show <em>&ldquo;Confirmed via [registry] registry&rdquo;</em> with a link to the source record.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-stone-200">
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 font-semibold mb-2">Layer 3</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Provider self-attestation</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Health testing results, program history, business policies, and any credential without Layer 2 passthrough are the provider\u2019s own attestation. BreederHQ does not open, read, or vouch for any uploaded document.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">
            BreederHQ may also display Profile Indicators based on account history on the platform (joined date, typical response time, completed transactions, open disputes). Indicators are facts about platform behavior, not endorsements.
          </p>
